jobs.title: Sr. React Developer
jobs.description: We are seeking a passionate and creative Front-End Developer to join our team. You will be responsible for translating UI/UX designs into responsive web interfaces using modern technologies like React, HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The ideal candidate has a good eye for design, strong coding skills, and a willingness to learn and grow in a fast-paced environment.
